Forex Trading Signal AI Agent
Project Report
Renu Shokeen
July 14, 2026


1 Executive Summary

The Forex Trading Signal AI Agent is an intelligent financial analytics platform de-
signed to generate actionable trading signals in the foreign exchange market. The system
combines technical analysis, machine learning techniques, market indicators, and risk
management methodologies to assist traders in making data-driven trading decisions.
The project analyzes historical forex price data, identifies market trends, generates
buy/sell signals, evaluates risk exposure, and visualizes trading opportunities through an
interactive analytics framework. The primary objective is to improve trading decision-
making while minimizing emotional bias and enhancing risk-adjusted returns.



2 Problem Statement

Foreign exchange markets are highly volatile and influenced by numerous macroeconomic
and technical factors. Traders often face challenges such as:
• Market uncertainty
• Information overload
• Emotional decision-making
• Risk management difficulties
• Signal reliability concerns

The objective of this project is to develop an AI-powered trading signal agent capable
of:

1. Identifying market trends
2. Generating trading signals
3. Evaluating risk exposure
4. Providing decision support
5. Improving trading efficiency



3 Project Objectives

• Develop an automated forex signal generation system.
• Analyze historical currency price movements.
• Generate buy, sell, and hold recommendations.
• Evaluate signal performance.
• Implement risk management metrics.
• Visualize market behavior and trading opportunities.
• Create an extensible AI-based trading framework.




4 Dataset Description

The project utilizes historical foreign exchange market data including:
• Currency Pair
• Date and Time
• Open Price
• High Price
• Low Price
• Close Price
• Trading Volume

Example Currency Pairs:
• EUR/USD
• GBP/USD
• USD/JPY
• AUD/USD
• USD/CAD
• USD/CHF
The dataset forms the foundation for technical indicator calculation and signal gen-
eration.



