8 Feature Engineering

Features created include:
• Daily Returns
• Moving Averages
• Volatility
• RSI
• MACD
• Signal Line
• Price Momentum
• Bollinger Bands
These features are used by the signal generation engine.




9 Trading Signal Generation

Trading signals are generated based on technical indicator combinations.

9.1 Buy Signal
Generated when:
• Short-term MA crosses above Long-term MA
• RSI < 30
• Positive MACD crossover

9.2 Sell Signal
Generated when:
• Short-term MA crosses below Long-term MA
• RSI > 70
• Negative MACD crossover

9.3 Hold Signal
Generated when market conditions remain neutral.
10 AI Recommendation Engine
The AI Recommendation Engine evaluates:
• Trend Strength
• Volatility
• Signal Confidence
• Risk Exposure
• Historical Performance
Example recommendations:
• Strong Buy
• Buy
• Hold
• Sell
• Strong Sell




11 Risk Management Framework

Risk management is a critical component of successful trading.

11.1 Position Sizing
Determines optimal trade allocation.

11.2 Stop Loss
Protects against excessive losses.

11.3 Take Profit
Locks in gains when target levels are reached.

11.4 Risk-Reward Ratio
