15 Results

The AI Agent successfully:
• Identified market trends.
• Generated actionable trading signals.
• Reduced manual analysis effort.
• Improved decision consistency.
• Evaluated trade risk effectively.
• Provided interpretable recommendations.
Key outcomes:
• Enhanced signal quality.
• Better market monitoring.
• Improved risk-adjusted trading decisions.






16 Business Insights

Major insights obtained include:
1. Trend-following signals perform well during directional markets.
2. Volatility significantly impacts signal reliability.
3. Risk management improves long-term profitability.
4. Combining multiple indicators reduces false signals.
5. AI-assisted trading improves consistency.





17 Limitations

Current limitations include:
• Dependence on historical market data.
• No direct integration with live trading platforms.
• Limited macroeconomic event modeling.
• Market regime changes may impact performance.
• Slippage and transaction costs may affect actual returns.





18 Future Enhancements

Future developments may include:
